pendencies is invalid. Furthermore, the cluster data show definitively that stars experience a temporary epoch of reduced braking efficiency where \$P\_\{{\textbackslash}rm rot\}\$ stall, and that the duration of this epoch lasts longer for lower-mass stars.},
